39:44.917 --> 39:46.667
You knew something
was gonna happen.

39:46.667 --> 39:48.667
You knew something
was going down that day.

39:56.625 --> 39:59.834
Narrator:
<i> By bringing their guns</i>
<i> into Tombstone,</i>

39:59.834 --> 40:03.041
<i> Clanton's gang knows</i>
<i> they are provoking a fight.</i>

40:08.750 --> 40:10.542
What do you want
to do, Wyatt?

40:12.792 --> 40:14.792
Go get me Doc Holliday.

40:14.792 --> 40:16.000
Yes, sir.

40:44.667 --> 40:47.001
Isenberg:
