40:52.417 --> 40:55.500
<i> The Earps make the decision</i>
<i> to walk down there</i>

40:55.500 --> 40:56.875
and confront these guys.

40:59.583 --> 41:01.000
<i> The way to understand men</i>
<i> in this period</i>

41:01.000 --> 41:03.500
<i> is an honor culture.</i>

41:03.500 --> 41:04.834
<i> You have to be willing</i>
<i> to meet</i>

41:04.834 --> 41:06.750
any challenge to your honor
with violence,

41:06.750 --> 41:08.917
<i> otherwise you're a coward.</i>

41:12.750 --> 41:17.417
Narrator:
<i> Wyatt Earp is headed</i>
<i> to a showdown with Ike Clanton</i>

41:17.417 --> 41:19.667
<i> at the O.K. Corral.</i>

41:24.917 --> 41:27.875
Kirschner:
