<i> the three Earp brothers</i>

41:27.875 --> 41:31.667
and Doc Holliday marching down
the dusty streets of Tombstone

41:31.667 --> 41:35.542
<i> to confront the cowboys</i>
<i> at the O.K. Corral</i>

41:35.542 --> 41:38.083
has burned
into our mythology.

